{"tid":1423231,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"我老母變左黑黃","createTime":"2019-08-06T13:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T13:16:00.000Z","uid":289152,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"425fb2c62478e2c8f9be828fd669a6b5778d0670","tid":1423231,"uid":289152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:16:00.000Z","msg":"岩岩食晚飯，我老母話自己變左黑黃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我老母<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個死人吉野家，以後都唔幫襯，藍既。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我不嬲都話吉野家唔好食，份量又少。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我覺得我依家唔係深黃，係黑黃，深到變左黑色。琴日出左去（意指7區集會，我同我老母去左黃大仙），依家覺得班後生仔殺警都無問題。<br />\n<br />\n利申我老豆老母極深黃，成日睇城寨，戒左cctvb好耐。"}]}